    "For instance, these studies also conclude that most SLR tools employ relatively outdated AI techniques (Schmidt et al. 2023 (Schmidt et al., 2023)), as we will discuss more in detail in Sect. 6.1.",
    "The second threat concerns the exclusion of tools that were either under maintenance and unavailable for evaluation or had not been updated in the past ten years.",
    "This exclusion criterion might have omitted tools that, despite being inaccessible at the time of the review, could otherwise fulfil the inclusion criteria.",
    "These exclusions could potentially restrict the generalisability of our findings.",
